      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:3:123:4",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ رَجُلَيْنِ بَيْنَهُمَا أَمَةٌ فَزَوَّجَاهَا مِنْ رَجُلٍ ثُمَّ إِنَّ الرَّجُلَ اشْتَرَى بَعْضَ السَّهْمَيْنِ فَقَالَ حَرُمَتْ عَلَيْهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Muhammad Bin Ahmad, from Al Abbas Bin Marouf, from Al Hassan Bin Muhammad, from Zur’at, from Sama’at who said, ",
          "‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about two men between them was a slave girl. So they both got her married to a man. Then the man bought part of the two shares. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘She would be Prohibited unto him’."
        ]
      }
    }
